The following directory should be added to compiler include paths:

    /home/pi/Transferências/boost_1_69_0

The following directory should be added to linker library paths:

    /home/pi/Transferências/boost_1_69_0/stage/lib

g++ -I /home/pi/Transferências/boost_1_69_0 -L /home/pi/Transferências/boost_1_69_0/stage/lib -pthread -lpigpio -lpthread -lrt tcpserver.cpp -o server
